{"tid":935932,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大胃王每日要屙幾多屎？","createTime":"2018-12-10T11:39:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-10T11:47:44.000Z","uid":206120,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1b76f75c39b0d1bbd12c7f3350989437ee0fed52","tid":935932,"uid":206120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T11:39:50.000Z","msg":"假設正常人每日食三餐 <br />\n一日屙一次屎的話每次大概會屙200g左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大胃王每餐可以食到十人份嘅食物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁即係每次屙屎會屙到2kg<br />\n<br />\n一個唔好彩佢地便秘，幾日都屙唔出<br />\n到佢地積埋積埋一次過爆發 到底佢地屙出黎啲屎可唔可以填平個馬桶呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a978968a0c4f6c57fc728dd4ea36bc4e8f8b0467","tid":935932,"uid":192311,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T11:47:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ULNo2xxdtdo/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FULNo2xxdtdo%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=f3ecab79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先你睇睇馬桶結構，配合埋果日大胃王嘅屎質，你就可以得到答案"}]}